This entry is for Geffen company logo labels
In all identical to [r=8638781]


Printed inner sleeve with upside down monkey image, top opening.
1st issue, pressed by Sonopress, with embossed 'Clef' logo on B-Side centre label. The runouts are stamped


Catalog numbers:
GEF 24425 from upper and left spines;
GEF 24425-8 and DGC 24425 from inner sleeve;
GEF 24 425 and DGC-24 425 from disc labels.
